<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَجِيدِ}</span> ... ذِي المَجْدِ وَالشَّرَفِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَجْعٌ بَعِيدٌ}</span> ... رُجُوعٌ إِلَى الحَيَاةِ بَعْدَ المَوْتِ، بَعِيدُ الوُقُوعِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَنقُصُ}</span> ... تُفْنِي مِنْ أَجْسَادِهِمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كِتَابٌ حَفِيظٌ}</span> ... حَافِظٌ لِجَمِيعِ أَفْعَالِهِمْ؛ وَهُوَ اللَّوْحُ المَحْفُوظُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّرِيجٍ}</span> ... مُضْطَرِبٍ، مُخْتَلَطٍ، لَا يَثْبُتُونَ عَلَى شَيْءٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فُرُوجٍ}</span> ... فُتُوقٍ، وَشُقُوقٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَدَدْنَاهَا}</span> ... وَسَّعْنَاهَا، وَفَرَشْنَاهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَوَاسِيَ}</span> ... جِبَالًا ثَوَابِتَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَوْجٍ بَهِيجٍ}</span> ... نَوْعٍ حَسَنِ المَنْظَرِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَبْصِرَةً}</span> ... عِبْرَةً يَتَبَصَّرُ بِهَا مِنْ عَمَى الجَهْلِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّنِيبٍ}</span> ... رَجَّاعٍ إِلَى اللهِ تَعَالَى.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحَبَّ الْحَصِيدِ}</span> ... حَبَّ الزَّرْعِ الَّذِي يُحْصَدُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَاسِقَاتٍ}</span> ... طِوَالًا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَلْعٌ نَّضِيدٌ}</span> ... ثَمَرٌ مُتَرَاكِبٌ بَعْضُهُ فَوْقَ بَعْضٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الرَّسِّ}</span> ... البِئْرِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>